===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|alt=*毬-ball,𤥲}}
"Ball", earlier some "kind of jade". {{zh-ref|Bodman (1980)}} relates this to Wuming {{cog|za||klau<sup>A2</sup>|ball}}, and relates {{zh-l|俅|gem-adorned}} to {{cog|bo|གྲུ||lustre of gems}}. This character had a softened initial in {{cog|zhx-min-pro|-}}.

Originally written as {{zh-l|*毬}} (since Tang dynasty) when referring to a ball. The form {{lang|zh|球}} (since Qing dynasty) is now more common.

